  <p class="TweetTextSize TweetTextSize--normal js-tweet-text tweet-text" lang="en" data-aria-label-part="0">Eventually, the decent people in Labour have to realise that tweeting or writing a letter about how disappointed and angry you are isn't good enough. He is your leader. You advocate him governing our country. Like it or not, this is what, by association, you stand for.</p>

Dont think of it as Euro qualifiers. Theyre trying to give international football a shot in the arm and move away from meaningless friendlies. Its a good thing.</p>

      </li>
      <li class="embed-link js-actionEmbedTweet" data-nav="embed_tweet">
        <button type="button" class="dropdown-link">Embed Tweet</button>
      </li>
  </ul>
</div>

  </div>

  <p class="TweetTextSize TweetTextSize--normal js-tweet-text tweet-text" lang="en" data-aria-label-part="0">I made the shed I live in London's top-rated restaurant on TripAdvisor. Then I actually opened it. Ladies &amp; Gents, after months screening phone calls from begging customers, eat it up: The Shed At Dulwich <a href="https://t.co/LnvUB9WRwc" rel="nofollow noopener" dir="ltr" data-expanded-url="https://www.vice.com/en_uk/article/434gqw/i-made-my-shed-the-top-rated-restaurant-on-tripadvisor?utm_campaign=sharebutton" class="twitter-timeline-link" target="_blank" title="https://www.vice.com/en_uk/article/434gqw/i-made-my-shed-the-top-rated-restaurant-on-tripadvisor?utm_campaign=sharebutton"><span class="tco-ellipsis"></span><span class="invisible">https://www.</span><span class="js-display-url">vice.com/en_uk/article/</span><span class="invisible">434gqw/i-made-my-shed-the-top-rated-restaurant-on-tripadvisor?utm_campaign=sharebutton</span><span class="tco-ellipsis"><span class="invisible"></span></span></a> <a href="/VICEUK" class="twitter-atreply pretty-link js-nav" dir="ltr" data-mentioned-user-id="15995155"><s>@</s><b>viceuk</b></a> <a href="/VICE" class="twitter-atreply pretty-link js-nav" dir="ltr" data-mentioned-user-id="23818581"><s>@</s><b>vice</b></a></p>
</div>

          <p class="u-hiddenVisually" aria-hidden="true" data-aria-label-part="1">Mark Wallace Retweeted Christopher Hope <span class="Emoji Emoji--forLinks" style="background-image:url('https://abs.twimg.com/emoji/v2/72x72/1f4dd.png')" title="Memo" aria-label="Emoji: Memo"></span><span class="visuallyhidden" aria-hidden="true"></span></p>


<div class="js-tweet-text-container">
  <p class="TweetTextSize TweetTextSize--normal js-tweet-text tweet-text" lang="en" data-aria-label-part="4">I and plenty of others have been saying this for over a year, for the good reason that it's obvious.<a href="https://t.co/pV0DLXqs7c" rel="nofollow noopener" dir="ltr" data-expanded-url="https://twitter.com/christopherhope/status/930113752975933447" class="twitter-timeline-link u-hidden" target="_blank" title="https://twitter.com/christopherhope/status/930113752975933447"><span class="tco-ellipsis"></span><span class="invisible">https://</span><span class="js-display-url">twitter.com/christopherhop</span><span class="invisible">e/status/930113752975933447</span><span class="tco-ellipsis"><span class="invisible"></span></span></a></p>

  <div class="QuoteTweet-originalAuthor u-cf u-textTruncate stream-item-header account-group js-user-profile-link">
    <b class="QuoteTweet-fullname u-linkComplex-target">Christopher Hope <span class="Emoji Emoji--forLinks" style="background-image:url('https://abs.twimg.com/emoji/v2/72x72/1f4dd.png')" title="Memo" aria-label="Emoji: Memo"></span><span class="visuallyhidden" aria-hidden="true"></span></b><span class="UserBadges"><span class="Icon Icon--verified"><span class="u-hiddenVisually">Verified account</span></span></span><span class="UserNameBreak"></span><span class="username u-dir u-textTruncate" dir="ltr">@<b>christopherhope</b></span>
  </div>

          
          
          <div class="QuoteTweet-text tweet-text u-dir" lang="en" data-aria-label-part="2" dir="ltr">BREAKING Britain will leave the EU without a deal if MPs vote down final deal, David Davis said. MPs in the House of Commons audibly gasped.</div>

      <div class="QuoteTweet&#10;    &#10;    &#10;    u-block js-tweet-details-fixer">
  <div class="QuoteTweet-container">
    <a class="QuoteTweet-link js-nav" href="/Oobahs/status/918072564349636611" data-conversation-id="918072564349636611" aria-hidden="true">
    </a>
    <div class="QuoteTweet-innerContainer u-cf js-permalink js-media-container" data-item-id="918072564349636611" data-item-type="tweet" data-screen-name="Oobahs" data-user-id="106936218" href="/Oobahs/status/918072564349636611" data-conversation-id="918072564349636611" tabindex="0">
      <div class="tweet-content">
        <div class="QuoteTweet-authorAndText u-alignTop">
            
  <div class="QuoteTweet-originalAuthor u-cf u-textTruncate stream-item-header account-group js-user-profile-link">
    <b class="QuoteTweet-fullname u-linkComplex-target">Oobah Butler</b><span class="UserBadges"><span class="Icon Icon--verified"><span class="u-hiddenVisually">Verified account</span></span></span><span class="UserNameBreak"></span><span class="username u-dir u-textTruncate" dir="ltr">@<b>Oobahs</b></span>
  </div>

          
          
          <div class="QuoteTweet-text tweet-text u-dir" lang="en" data-aria-label-part="2" dir="ltr">Knockoff brands you see on markets? Well, I became one &amp; made it top of Paris fashion. </div>

</div>

  </div>

      </div>
